{"tid":965344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣現「馬路陷阱」，車輛遭鐵蒺藜刺中爆胎","createTime":"2019-01-02T03:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T10:04:21.000Z","uid":105678,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa90e5fb299c6727ac1424e06c5994e352545a9","tid":965344,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190101/s00001/63be2c69f61df5f6c416127f40ebdf83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190101%2Fs00001%2F63be2c69f61df5f6c416127f40ebdf83.jpg&h=d7d87729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣近日出現「馬路陷阱」。自周日（12月30日）起，網民先後發現，青山公路深井至汀九段，及荃灣禾笛街路面都放有鐵蒺藜，遂拍照上載至社交網站，提醒區內車主。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣汀深區區議員鄭捷彬回應本報查詢時指，周日接獲一名「中招」車主投訴，指車輛在青山公路深井段遭鐵蒺藜刺中車胎，他遂代為報案，其後再陸續接獲逾10名居民反映關注。鄭盼警方早日破案，以免再有車輛遭殃。"},{"pid":"0e523a3868f17d2896d0daaaedf9ee814fd01eb0","tid":965344,"uid":161374,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"似係佐助去完荃灣跌咗"},{"pid":"3fa3ca2230d3e8dd6aa89d25cb81bbc3f3b4e582","tid":965344,"uid":41974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"暴力減速帶"},{"pid":"a04660854b6eb83b882c5f9313597306bbbb5b25","tid":965344,"uid":57205,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:34:44.000Z","msg":"99%拖車狗放"},{"pid":"9a8daeabfd75a1d82c9447d60548d1d3ef98c7f7","tid":965344,"uid":5490,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"need for speed"},{"pid":"85f34796744c0ed62e938f5a2d6e136c4049eee6","tid":965344,"uid":122139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e523a3868f17d2896d0daaaedf9ee814fd01eb0","tid":965344,"uid":161374,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"似係佐助去完荃灣跌咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.g